      "rationale": "Validation experiments were conducted at five operating points spanning 2–6 L/min and 2000–3200 RPM, which are contained within the COU operating envelope. Temperature, fluid viscosity (bovine blood analogue), and inlet pressure conditions were documented and matched to simulation boundary conditions within measurement uncertainty."
    },
    {
