      "rationale": "Predicted NIH values were compared against experimentally measured values at all five operating points. The maximum deviation was 11.4% and the mean absolute error was 7.8%, both within the 15% acceptance criterion. Pressure-flow curve predictions agreed within 6% of measured values across the full speed range."
